WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.000
NYUAD provides financial support in the form of fellowships and need-based grants, to those who qualify

00:05.000 --> 00:16.000
The support may cover up to the full cost of attendance, including tuition, foreign travel for study integral to a student's academic program, room and board, health insurance, personal expenses, books, and many student life activities

00:16.000 --> 00:23.000
Financial support may also include up to two tickets each year between Abu Dhabi and the student's country of permanent residence

